    <description>
        <en>
<![CDATA[A homestead-sized bandsaw mill for your farm - two different production versions or an easy to use sellpoint!

The Platinum DLC is required, but only needs to be enabled to produce Long Planks & Wood Beams.

Placement Note: If you wish to place a shed over the sawmill - place the shed first, then using free-placement mode, place the sawmill under the shed.

For license & feedback, please visit: https://github.com/GMNGjoy/FS22_BandsawMill]]>
		</en>
        <de>
<![CDATA[Ein Bandsägewerk für's eigene Gehöft - zwei verschiedene Produtkionsvarianten oder eine einfach zu verwendende Verkaufsstation

Besucht für Lizenz & Feedback bitte https://github.com/GMNGjoy/FS22_BandsawMill]]>
        </de>
